05-02T07:07:07.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>但他認為無拘束的資本主義新領域在中國。在審判中拿出的一段2009年的電話錄音裡，布蘭肯希普表示他可能會搬到亞洲，因為那裡的政府管制較少。<br />\n...<br />\n中國人搞的是獨裁資本主義，它非常有效。這就是企業運營的方式。企業並不是一種民主體制。</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n一個奸一個賤, 襯到絕"},{"pid":"f15037b469b6d90a62c00b62571d0e14901aa847","tid":647890,"uid":134071,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"3400b901e0f015c9bfb2d77fb9f751fe039436ed","tid":647890,"uid":24730,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"f08e8a95ca28cd552cc7b5c6c73956d80daa6bb1","tid":647890,"uid":134071,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-05-02T05:12:15.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>個老婆好明顯係間諜</blockquote>好多西方男人都輸比中國女間諜<br />\n<br />\n梅鐸 (共和黨大<strong>金</strong>主)都衰係鄧文迪身上<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote>"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-05-02T06:34:40.000Z","msg":"仲有Facebook 個豬佬"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-05-02T07:33:54.000Z","msg":"有時真係好難怪佢地<br />\n<br />\n大陸妹既異性吸引力可能係世界頂級<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  好多唔鍾意大陸人既男士, 都鍾意大陸妹<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c9b8dad67cd566814a8ad79a259a3808e38a2cad","tid":647890,"uid":21545,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-05-02T07:36:45.000Z","msg":"又係強國飛機文<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d5d6fd49820af7ea4416e6cc10342d042c3addf9","tid":647890,"uid":134071,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"c9b8dad67cd566814a8ad79a259a3808e38a2cad","tid":647890,"uid":21545,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-05-02T07:36:45.000Z","msg":"又係強國飛機文<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-05-02T07:37:51.000Z","msg":"New York Times報導...."},{"pid":"7f9a1ac70cba4d42085f85149f6f7cc32a9d387b","tid":647890,"uid":34103,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-02T07:39:31.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"750264f4f37a7247d791bc8395c